01:31.473 --> 01:34.520
(I bought an apartment
next to the studio.)

01:35.492 --> 01:36.751
I will not lie to you.

01:38.812 --> 01:42.592
Qiang Qingci won't lie
to Shengshengman either.

01:51.276 --> 01:56.224
